485
00:37:43,590 --> 00:37:44,951
We've been separated for five years.

486
00:37:44,951 --> 00:37:48,590
This is your first time paying respect to the ancestors after coming back.

487
00:37:49,531 --> 00:37:53,531
I'm to blame for not staying in the capital to do my duty as a daughter.

488
00:37:53,531 --> 00:37:56,731
It's fine. Your great-grandmother has always been kind to her children.

489
00:37:56,731 --> 00:37:58,950
She won't blame you.

490
00:38:02,368 --> 00:38:03,611
   

491
00:38:03,611 --> 00:38:07,250
Great-grandmother is the only woman monarch in the dynasty.

492
00:38:07,250 --> 00:38:12,090
I heard that during her reign, she first allowed females to take part in the imperial exam.

493
00:38:12,090 --> 00:38:14,110
Yes, she did.

494
00:38:14,110 --> 00:38:17,950
I'm just following in her footsteps.

495
00:38:21,110 --> 00:38:25,510
Father, your decision is the greatest grace for all women.

496
00:38:26,331 --> 00:38:31,890
If I weren't a princess, I'd like to partake in the imperial examinations as a commoner.

497
00:38:31,890 --> 00:38:37,571
Perhaps I could realize my ambitions like Great-Grandmother did.

498
00:38:37,571 --> 00:38:42,551
Instead, I would prefer you to lead a happy life.

499
00:38:42,551 --> 00:38:46,650
Among my children, you're my favorite.

500
00:38:46,650 --> 00:38:51,111
Also, I feel so sorry for you in particular.

501
00:38:51,851 --> 00:38:53,890
Why do you say so, Father?

502
00:38:54,831 --> 00:38:57,431
You lost your mother when you were little and had been staying in Jiangnan.

503
00:38:57,431 --> 00:39:02,131
Of all my children, you're the only one who didn't stay with me.

504
00:39:02,131 --> 00:39:07,250
And when your husband was chosen, Xue Xiaotang died in the war at Juma River.

505
00:39:08,291 --> 00:39:14,591
Come to think of it, you've been alone all these years and moving around.

506
00:39:14,591 --> 00:39:18,570
I owe you too much.

507
00:39:19,650 --> 00:39:21,850
Please don't say that, Father.

508
00:39:21,850 --> 00:39:24,051
Though I've been living in Jiangnan alone,

509
00:39:24,051 --> 00:39:30,131
